1
00:00:29,605 --> 00:00:35,765
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

2
00:01:55,725 --> 00:01:58,325
EPISODE 13

3
00:02:03,365 --> 00:02:04,725
Your phone, sir.

4
00:02:05,605 --> 00:02:06,965
Hello?

5
00:02:07,685 --> 00:02:08,645
Is that you, Qingqing?

6
00:02:09,245 --> 00:02:10,085
Grandpa.

7
00:02:10,525 --> 00:02:12,085
I miss you.

8
00:02:12,165 --> 00:02:15,565
I thought you went away for a while
because you were upset.

9
00:02:15,644 --> 00:02:18,725
I didn't think you'd be gone for months.

10
00:02:19,285 --> 00:02:21,565
Qingqing, listen to me.

11
00:02:22,205 --> 00:02:23,685
If you come back,

12
00:02:23,765 --> 00:02:25,445
I will do anything for you.

13
00:02:25,525 --> 00:02:26,885
Then please,

14
00:02:27,325 --> 00:02:28,925
in the name of my mom,

15
00:02:29,005 --> 00:02:31,205
tell me the truth.

16
00:02:32,325 --> 00:02:37,685
Have you been lying to me
about Mom and Dad?

17
00:02:39,285 --> 00:02:41,885
I had to hide some things from you

18
00:02:42,125 --> 00:02:43,685
for your own good.

19
00:02:43,765 --> 00:02:44,685
I was so--

20
00:02:45,725 --> 00:02:48,885
What did Qingqing find out
that she'd ask something like this?

21
00:02:49,405 --> 00:02:52,365
She must have gone
to her parents' college after all.

22
00:02:55,325 --> 00:02:57,605
You were alone with that witch
for so long.

23
00:02:57,765 --> 00:02:59,085
Weren't you scared?

24
00:02:59,165 --> 00:03:00,765
You mean, Ms. Chen?

25
00:03:00,965 --> 00:03:02,965
-Ms. Chen?
-Yeah.

26
00:03:03,045 --> 00:03:04,965
You're now calling her Ms. Chen
behind her back?

27
00:03:05,965 --> 00:03:07,325
Did she plant a bug on you?

28
00:03:08,885 --> 00:03:13,045
Fangfang, this time,
I really got to know Ms. Chen.

29
00:03:13,125 --> 00:03:15,045
She's a good person.

30
00:03:16,325 --> 00:03:17,885
Did she cast a spell on you?

31
00:03:19,445 --> 00:03:21,765
Qingqing, it's my day off tomorrow.

32
00:03:21,845 --> 00:03:22,965
Do you want to hang out?

33
00:03:24,245 --> 00:03:28,445
No. Tomorrow, I have
a date with a mysterious person.

34
00:03:28,885 --> 00:03:31,125
-A mysterious person?
-Yeah.

35
00:03:32,125 --> 00:03:33,565
Is it Situ Feng?

36
00:03:33,645 --> 00:03:36,245
The both of you were so in character
during the play.

37
00:03:36,325 --> 00:03:38,125
The more you acted,
the more real it seemed.

38
00:03:38,205 --> 00:03:40,725
-You kissed like real lovers--
-Knock it off, Fangfang!

39
00:03:41,365 --> 00:03:42,445
Gosh!

40
00:03:43,005 --> 00:03:46,445
I see that you're getting even more...

41
00:03:46,525 --> 00:03:47,845
What?

42
00:03:47,925 --> 00:03:48,805
Gossipy.

43
00:03:48,885 --> 00:03:50,445
Come here.

44
00:03:50,525 --> 00:03:52,045
I need to ask you something.

45
00:03:52,205 --> 00:03:53,045
Sit.

46
00:03:54,165 --> 00:03:55,005
I want to ask you.

47
00:03:55,085 --> 00:03:58,645
What's really going on between you
and Lin Yiyang?

48
00:03:59,765 --> 00:04:01,085
Don't tell me you like him.

49
00:04:02,165 --> 00:04:04,605
But he used to kidnap us, Fangfang.

50
00:04:04,685 --> 00:04:06,005
No!

51
00:04:06,485 --> 00:04:09,325
I just think that sometimes,
he's pretending.

52
00:04:09,925 --> 00:04:10,925
It makes me curious.

53
00:04:13,165 --> 00:04:14,685
Someone in this dormitory

54
00:04:14,925 --> 00:04:16,845
has fallen in love.

55
00:04:16,925 --> 00:04:18,285
Cut it out!

56
00:04:18,845 --> 00:04:20,365
Like I said, about you and Situ Feng,

57
00:04:20,445 --> 00:04:23,205
you were so into it
when you were on stage.

58
00:04:23,565 --> 00:04:24,964
Your relationship developed so fast.

59
00:04:25,045 --> 00:04:26,605
Cut the crap already.

60
00:04:26,685 --> 00:04:28,565
He's just one of the good-looks club.

61
00:04:28,645 --> 00:04:30,885
I look down on him, he surrenders to me.

62
00:04:30,965 --> 00:04:34,965
There's already so much hatred between us.
There's no way for us to like each other.

63
00:04:35,045 --> 00:04:37,045
That's not necessarily the case.

64
00:04:37,365 --> 00:04:39,525
I remember an author once said,

65
00:04:39,605 --> 00:04:41,245
"If we judge love,

66
00:04:41,325 --> 00:04:43,485
by the majority of its results,
it resembles hatred

67
00:04:43,565 --> 00:04:44,965
more than friendship."

68
00:04:45,445 --> 00:04:47,645
Then the author was just fooling around.

69
00:04:47,725 --> 00:04:50,365
But then again,
I want to ask you something.

70
00:04:50,965 --> 00:04:53,525
How would I know

71
00:04:54,365 --> 00:04:57,045
if I'm in love with somebody?

72
00:04:58,125 --> 00:05:01,165
I've never talked about love,
but as they say in the books,

73
00:05:01,765 --> 00:05:03,285
"When you can completely

74
00:05:03,365 --> 00:05:05,365
be your own self in front of someone,

75
00:05:05,645 --> 00:05:07,325
that means you're in love with him."

76
00:05:08,525 --> 00:05:10,365
So what if I'm not myself,

77
00:05:11,085 --> 00:05:13,565
but I've turned into
a completely different person?

78
00:05:13,645 --> 00:05:15,605
Maybe you aren't
a completely different person,

79
00:05:15,765 --> 00:05:17,285
but you've discovered your true self.

80
00:05:20,685 --> 00:05:23,525
Fangfang, no one could've thought of that.

81
00:05:23,885 --> 00:05:26,885
You could wipe out all the so-called
love experts on Weibo!

82
00:05:26,965 --> 00:05:28,325
You're brilliant!

83
00:05:28,885 --> 00:05:30,525
I want to ask you too.

84
00:05:30,725 --> 00:05:31,765
Have you ever thought of

85
00:05:32,485 --> 00:05:34,565
what kind of guy do you like?

86
00:05:36,165 --> 00:05:37,005
I like...

87
00:05:43,085 --> 00:05:44,165
By the way,

88
00:05:44,245 --> 00:05:46,365
my grandma's birthday is in a few days.

89
00:05:47,045 --> 00:05:49,045
Can you come and help me
carry the gifts tomorrow?

90
00:05:49,125 --> 00:05:50,285
Okay.

91
00:05:50,485 --> 00:05:53,445
I've been doing the same thing every year.
Why are you even asking?

92
00:05:53,525 --> 00:05:55,245
I asked

93
00:05:55,685 --> 00:05:58,445
simply to remind you
that another year has passed,

94
00:05:58,525 --> 00:05:59,965
and I still don't have a girlfriend.

95
00:06:00,685 --> 00:06:03,205
You're a good guy.
There will be someone for you.

96
00:06:03,285 --> 00:06:04,245
Don't give up.

97
00:06:04,725 --> 00:06:07,925
I heard that the whole campus

98
00:06:08,645 --> 00:06:10,925
is asking me about my sexual orientation.

99
00:06:11,405 --> 00:06:12,925
Of course.

100
00:06:13,365 --> 00:06:15,525
You're warm, you're hygienic

101
00:06:15,605 --> 00:06:17,565
and you don't have bad habits.

102
00:06:17,925 --> 00:06:20,565
No one would believe it
if you said you were straight.

103
00:06:21,525 --> 00:06:23,285
If they doubt your sexual orientation,

104
00:06:23,445 --> 00:06:24,685
who do they think you're with?

105
00:06:31,405 --> 00:06:32,405
Gu Nanxi.

106
00:06:32,765 --> 00:06:34,405
You should keep looking for a girlfriend.

107
00:06:34,925 --> 00:06:36,325
Why are you always sticking with me?

108
00:06:36,405 --> 00:06:37,725
Don't tell me...

109
00:06:38,165 --> 00:06:39,725
Do you really like me?

110
00:06:39,805 --> 00:06:42,725
I don't have freckles
and I don't have curly hair.

111
00:06:42,805 --> 00:06:44,365
I don't go around baring my fangs

112
00:06:44,445 --> 00:06:46,285
and I don't speak with a thundering voice.

113
00:06:47,685 --> 00:06:49,285
How am I supposed

114
00:06:49,765 --> 00:06:52,005
to attract you, Your Highness?

115
00:06:52,285 --> 00:06:53,485
Get out.

116
00:06:55,645 --> 00:06:57,485
You can make a date with Qingchen.

117
00:07:05,565 --> 00:07:08,365
I've tried so many times, but I couldn't.

118
00:07:08,565 --> 00:07:09,445
So I gave up.

119
00:07:09,525 --> 00:07:11,565
Why is that?

120
00:07:11,645 --> 00:07:13,205
Beats me.

121
00:07:13,765 --> 00:07:15,885
I'm so done talking to you about love.

122
00:07:16,245 --> 00:07:17,765
I'll come with you tomorrow.

123
00:07:21,845 --> 00:07:24,245
That place was really huge and lively.

124
00:07:24,325 --> 00:07:26,085
Next thing you know, when he dropped by,

125
00:07:26,165 --> 00:07:27,805
we have already finished our meal.

126
00:07:27,885 --> 00:07:29,365
Your dad was left eating by himself.

127
00:07:29,445 --> 00:07:30,285
Really?

128
00:07:30,365 --> 00:07:31,245
Really.

129
00:07:32,085 --> 00:07:33,005
Ms. Chen.

130
00:07:33,645 --> 00:07:35,645
I really want to thank you

131
00:07:35,725 --> 00:07:39,045
for being able to tell me so much
about my parents today.

132
00:07:41,005 --> 00:07:43,445
Qingqing, shall we meet up again
next time?

133
00:07:43,925 --> 00:07:45,365
Sure. You should hurry back now.

134
00:07:45,445 --> 00:07:46,525
I'll pay the bills.

135
00:07:46,605 --> 00:07:47,685
Okay, I've got to go.

136
00:08:00,445 --> 00:08:01,605
Hey, Nanxi.

137
00:08:02,245 --> 00:08:03,685
Isn't that Qingchen?

138
00:08:03,765 --> 00:08:05,085
We just ran into her like this.

139
00:08:05,605 --> 00:08:06,605
Come on, let's go there.

140
00:08:07,045 --> 00:08:07,885
-No.
-Come on.

141
00:08:07,965 --> 00:08:09,885
-Forget it.
-Come on.

142
00:08:11,925 --> 00:08:13,285
Hey, Qingchen.

143
00:08:15,845 --> 00:08:17,005
What a coincidence.

144
00:08:17,365 --> 00:08:18,725
It sure is.

145
00:08:18,805 --> 00:08:20,085
What brings you here?

146
00:08:20,165 --> 00:08:21,005
Do you mind?

147
00:08:22,285 --> 00:08:23,445
No, I don't.

148
00:08:25,285 --> 00:08:26,125
Qingchen.

149
00:08:26,205 --> 00:08:27,485
Are you busy after this?

150
00:08:27,885 --> 00:08:28,725
Yes.

151
00:08:30,085 --> 00:08:31,845
How about a little chit-chat?

152
00:08:32,005 --> 00:08:34,325
It won't take up too much of your time.

153
00:08:36,525 --> 00:08:37,725
Don't bother her.

154
00:08:38,284 --> 00:08:40,445
Miss Qingchen, I'm sorry to bother you.

155
00:08:40,684 --> 00:08:42,164
Situ Feng is going through

156
00:08:42,245 --> 00:08:44,525
some sort of love-hate relationship
with a girl on campus.

157
00:08:44,645 --> 00:08:47,804
So he's a little outgoing
and not quite like himself.

158
00:08:48,525 --> 00:08:49,565
Hey, Gu Nanxi!

159
00:08:49,685 --> 00:08:50,725
What are you talking about?

160
00:08:50,805 --> 00:08:52,405
I want to go buy some gifts.

161
00:08:52,485 --> 00:08:54,885
You guys should have a chat.
I've got to go.

162
00:08:55,045 --> 00:08:56,525
Hey, Gu Nanxi.

163
00:09:02,685 --> 00:09:03,725
Never mind.

164
00:09:03,845 --> 00:09:04,725
Well...

165
00:09:04,845 --> 00:09:05,685
My friend...

166
00:09:05,765 --> 00:09:09,325
-He's a really nice guy.
-Yeah, I can tell.

167
00:09:09,405 --> 00:09:10,285
They call you

168
00:09:10,365 --> 00:09:12,565
"Your Coldhearted Highness."

169
00:09:13,205 --> 00:09:16,565
But, you don't look as cold as they say.

170
00:09:17,805 --> 00:09:18,805
Do you think so?

171
00:09:18,885 --> 00:09:20,085
Yeah.

172
00:09:20,165 --> 00:09:21,485
By the way,

173
00:09:22,245 --> 00:09:24,165
Gu Nanxi just said

174
00:09:24,245 --> 00:09:26,565
you have a love-hate relationship
with someone.

175
00:09:27,205 --> 00:09:28,285
Who's that someone?

176
00:09:28,845 --> 00:09:30,045
A crazy friend of mine.

177
00:09:31,965 --> 00:09:32,885
But,

178
00:09:33,405 --> 00:09:34,725
I realized that

179
00:09:35,365 --> 00:09:37,245
I can be myself in front of her

180
00:09:37,805 --> 00:09:39,245
more comfortably than before.

181
00:09:39,325 --> 00:09:41,005
"When you can completely

182
00:09:41,085 --> 00:09:43,205
be your own self in front of someone,

183
00:09:43,525 --> 00:09:45,005
that means you're in love with him."

184
00:09:47,845 --> 00:09:50,685
It looks like this friend of yours

185
00:09:51,365 --> 00:09:53,765
is more than just a friend.

186
00:09:55,685 --> 00:09:56,605
Yeah.

187
00:09:57,685 --> 00:10:01,045
She is more than just a friend to me.

188
00:10:01,885 --> 00:10:02,725
She's...

189
00:10:04,205 --> 00:10:05,525
my best friend.

190
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,325
You should meet her sometime.

191
00:10:07,405 --> 00:10:10,085
You've got to teach her
to be more ladylike.

192
00:10:12,845 --> 00:10:15,565
Even so, it's nothing, really.

193
00:10:16,085 --> 00:10:17,205
I think you should

194
00:10:17,765 --> 00:10:18,965
get to know each other.

195
00:10:19,365 --> 00:10:22,645
I see that your behavior
is a bit similar to hers.

196
00:10:22,725 --> 00:10:24,005
I find that odd.

197
00:10:27,685 --> 00:10:30,685
If you'll excuse me,
I have something to attend to.

198
00:10:30,765 --> 00:10:32,765
Say goodbye to Nanxi for me. Bye.

199
00:10:36,485 --> 00:10:37,645
Nanxi is...

200
00:10:43,525 --> 00:10:44,725
That was close!

201
00:10:45,285 --> 00:10:48,325
It makes me uncomfortable every time
I make up as Qingchen.

202
00:10:48,725 --> 00:10:51,565
Then I met Situ Feng
and I don't know how to talk to him.

203
00:10:52,125 --> 00:10:55,645
But then again, Qingchen is the real me.

204
00:10:57,005 --> 00:11:00,645
Why should I be angry
when he's stepping on Qingqing?

205
00:11:01,405 --> 00:11:02,245
Gosh.

206
00:11:02,325 --> 00:11:06,165
Chen Qingqing,
you've got a split personality!

207
00:11:27,885 --> 00:11:28,925
Hey.

208
00:11:30,445 --> 00:11:32,725
Qingqing, what a coincidence.

209
00:11:32,885 --> 00:11:34,125
What are you doing here?

210
00:11:34,205 --> 00:11:35,965
Weren't you having coffee just now?

211
00:11:38,285 --> 00:11:40,205
Hey, how did you know that?

212
00:11:42,245 --> 00:11:45,245
Look, there's a coffee mark
at the side of your mouth.

213
00:11:45,525 --> 00:11:47,245
Not only you can't control your limbs,

214
00:11:47,325 --> 00:11:48,845
you can't use your brain either!

215
00:11:48,925 --> 00:11:50,525
Tell me, what are you doing here?

216
00:11:51,325 --> 00:11:52,525
Doing some shopping.

217
00:11:52,605 --> 00:11:53,445
And you?

218
00:11:54,645 --> 00:11:57,405
I'm here to look for a part-time job.

219
00:11:58,045 --> 00:11:59,565
Have you found one?

220
00:12:00,325 --> 00:12:01,845
It's hard to get one here.

221
00:12:02,005 --> 00:12:04,565
Chen Qingqing, don't you earn enough
from being my assistant?

222
00:12:04,645 --> 00:12:06,725
Besides, if anyone catches you,
you'll embarrass me.

223
00:12:06,805 --> 00:12:07,725
All right.

224
00:12:08,365 --> 00:12:09,605
What a bother.

225
00:12:09,685 --> 00:12:11,685
We can't help you get a part-time job.

226
00:12:11,765 --> 00:12:13,805
But we can help you
save on your travel expenses.

227
00:12:13,885 --> 00:12:14,925
Let's go.

228
00:12:21,965 --> 00:12:23,965
-Qingqing!
-Yes?

229
00:12:24,045 --> 00:12:26,805
-I heard you're from Jincheng.
-Yes.

230
00:12:26,885 --> 00:12:29,685
We haven't properly
introduced you to Yuncheng.

231
00:12:29,765 --> 00:12:32,245
We should come out
and enjoy ourselves more often.

232
00:12:34,525 --> 00:12:37,925
Don't you know,
ever since I came to this college,

233
00:12:38,005 --> 00:12:40,325
I kept running into sixes and sevens
without fail.

234
00:12:40,405 --> 00:12:42,285
So I have no time to relax.

235
00:12:42,365 --> 00:12:44,725
But my grandma's birthday is coming up.

236
00:12:44,805 --> 00:12:46,485
Would you like to join me?

237
00:12:47,085 --> 00:12:47,965
Yeah.

238
00:12:48,045 --> 00:12:49,805
You've got to relax sometimes.

239
00:12:50,605 --> 00:12:52,405
Can I bring Fangfang along?

240
00:12:53,005 --> 00:12:54,805
Of course, you can.

241
00:13:00,285 --> 00:13:02,565
Qingqing, do you have an evening dress?

242
00:13:03,085 --> 00:13:04,205
Maybe I can buy you one.

243
00:13:04,285 --> 00:13:05,365
Oh, no, thank you.

244
00:13:05,765 --> 00:13:06,925
I hate that stuff.

245
00:13:07,005 --> 00:13:08,045
Look at you.

246
00:13:08,565 --> 00:13:10,725
I simply can't put up with you.

247
00:13:10,805 --> 00:13:12,525
If I put on an evening dress,

248
00:13:12,805 --> 00:13:14,205
you're going to freak out!

249
00:13:15,925 --> 00:13:16,765
Step on it.

250
00:13:19,485 --> 00:13:23,645
May you lead a life full of joy,
live long and smile always!

251
00:13:23,725 --> 00:13:24,565
Thank you.

252
00:13:25,245 --> 00:13:26,085
Sure.

253
00:13:29,885 --> 00:13:30,725
Grandma.

254
00:13:30,885 --> 00:13:32,325
-Happy birthday.
-Thank you.

255
00:13:32,405 --> 00:13:36,005
Mom and I would like to wish you
to be always healthy and cheerful.

256
00:13:39,205 --> 00:13:41,285
This piece of jade represents good luck.

257
00:13:41,365 --> 00:13:43,285
It'd be good for you to put it on.

258
00:13:43,365 --> 00:13:44,725
This is for you, Grandma.

259
00:13:44,885 --> 00:13:46,365
-Good one.
-Happy birthday, Mother.

260
00:13:46,445 --> 00:13:47,445
Thank you.

261
00:13:48,045 --> 00:13:49,165
It's a jade bracelet.

262
00:13:49,245 --> 00:13:50,525
It doesn't look that great.

263
00:13:51,405 --> 00:13:54,405
Grandma, look at what I got you here.

264
00:13:54,565 --> 00:13:56,165
A five-carat diamond necklace.

265
00:13:56,765 --> 00:13:59,165
I wish you longevity, Grandma.

266
00:13:59,885 --> 00:14:01,245
Here you go, Grandma.

267
00:14:01,325 --> 00:14:02,245
Good boy.

268
00:14:02,725 --> 00:14:04,645
As long as you gave them to me,

269
00:14:04,765 --> 00:14:06,285
that would keep me happy.

270
00:14:06,365 --> 00:14:08,965
Well, Grandma, please excuse us.

271
