Look at the context, all right?

543
00:28:03,445 --> 00:28:04,685
What I meant by "like" is,

544
00:28:04,765 --> 00:28:06,805
what I admire, what I appreciate

545
00:28:06,885 --> 00:28:08,085
and what I envy about you.

546
00:28:08,805 --> 00:28:10,685
You're so good at languages,

547
00:28:10,765 --> 00:28:13,045
but why isn't your math as good?

548
00:28:14,005 --> 00:28:15,525
You're a retard.

549
00:28:29,085 --> 00:28:30,605
Hey. Situ Feng.

550
00:28:31,365 --> 00:28:33,005
Did you hear that?

551
00:28:39,525 --> 00:28:40,685
It must be a mouse.

552
00:28:40,925 --> 00:28:41,765
What?

553
00:28:42,445 --> 00:28:43,725
A mouse?

554
00:28:44,365 --> 00:28:46,165
Situ Feng, you've got to protect me!

555
00:28:47,005 --> 00:28:47,925
But how?

556
00:28:48,165 --> 00:28:52,165
Why do I always end up like this
every time I'm with you?

557
00:28:52,285 --> 00:28:53,125
I hate this!

558
00:28:53,205 --> 00:28:54,485
There's a mouse around here.

559
00:28:54,765 --> 00:28:56,685
You hate it? Let's go find it.

560
00:28:57,925 --> 00:29:01,085
Situ Feng, put me down!

561
00:29:01,165 --> 00:29:02,045
Look.

562
00:29:02,365 --> 00:29:03,565
Hurry, look.

563
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:13,525
It's not a mouse.

564
00:29:14,085 --> 00:29:15,685
It's a kitten.

565
00:29:22,925 --> 00:29:25,325
I like cats so much!

566
00:29:31,925 --> 00:29:33,485
Why do you like cats?

567
00:29:34,725 --> 00:29:38,125
Don't you have the ability
to think logically?

568
00:29:38,485 --> 00:29:40,125
I hate mice.

569
00:29:40,325 --> 00:29:41,685
Cats catch mice.

570
00:29:41,765 --> 00:29:43,485
So I like cats.

571
00:29:43,725 --> 00:29:45,005
Right?

572
00:29:45,685 --> 00:29:46,845
Little kitty.

573
00:29:46,925 --> 00:29:49,365
I want to take you home and keep you.

574
00:29:49,445 --> 00:29:50,645
Okay?

575
00:29:52,605 --> 00:29:54,325
Don't you want to give it a name?

576
00:29:54,685 --> 00:29:55,925
A name?

577
00:29:56,285 --> 00:29:57,125
Okay.

578
00:29:57,605 --> 00:29:58,805
How about

579
00:29:59,525 --> 00:30:01,365
I call you Kitty Chen?

580
00:30:01,485 --> 00:30:02,565
-You like it?
-Hey.

581
00:30:03,245 --> 00:30:05,445
Why is it a Chen, not a Situ like me?

582
00:30:05,525 --> 00:30:08,485
Can't you see my surname
is much more epic?

583
00:30:08,965 --> 00:30:09,965
Epic?

584
00:30:10,045 --> 00:30:11,565
Are you kidding me?

585
00:30:11,845 --> 00:30:14,365
We found this kitten together.

586
00:30:14,525 --> 00:30:16,285
We're the mom and dad.

587
00:30:16,365 --> 00:30:18,165
I'm the dad. You're the mom.

588
00:30:18,245 --> 00:30:19,565
Of course it'll take my surname.

589
00:30:19,765 --> 00:30:21,405
Am I right, Kitty Chen?

590
00:30:22,085 --> 00:30:23,165
That's right.

591
00:30:24,165 --> 00:30:25,045
-Hey.
-Yes?

592
00:30:25,165 --> 00:30:26,325
Why are you the dad?

593
00:30:27,165 --> 00:30:29,485
Because I'm domineering.

594
00:30:30,645 --> 00:30:31,685
Enough about that.

595
00:30:31,965 --> 00:30:34,085
We should at least give it a nickname.

596
00:30:34,165 --> 00:30:35,405
That would be...

597
00:30:37,005 --> 00:30:38,845
Situ's Stupid Dog!

598
00:30:39,845 --> 00:30:40,685
Hey.

599
00:30:56,245 --> 00:30:57,965
Chen Qingqing, what are you drawing?

600
00:30:59,125 --> 00:31:01,485
-Ming De's Yearly Miss Campus--
-Excuse me!

601
00:31:01,565 --> 00:31:02,845
Why are you here?

602
00:31:02,925 --> 00:31:05,285
I'm here to join the Miss Campus contest.

603
00:31:05,365 --> 00:31:08,765
Our Student Council Secretariat
received a letter of complaint earlier.

604
00:31:10,965 --> 00:31:12,245
You're doing this on purpose!

605
00:31:12,725 --> 00:31:17,125
I have something important to ask you.

606
00:31:17,205 --> 00:31:20,725
May I ask what motivated you
to stand on this stage?

607
00:31:20,805 --> 00:31:23,605
Based on your understanding,
what defines beauty?

608
00:31:23,685 --> 00:31:26,525
The winner
of Ming De College's Miss Campus is...

609
00:31:28,765 --> 00:31:30,685
Subtitle translation by CL Tan
